OL,3,CRod Stewart tells King he put 'ratbag'
OL,4,CTrump 'in his place' during state visit
OL,6,FSir Rod Stewart spoke to the King
OL,7,Fduring the 50th anniversary of the
OL,8,FKing's Trust at the Royal Albert Hall
OL,10,FSir Rod Stewart has congratulated the
OL,11,FKing for putting "that little ratbag
OL,12,Fin his place", appearing to reference
OL,13,FDonald Trump, who recently hosted
OL,14,FCharles on his state visit.
OL,16,FDuring a line-up in the interval of an
OL,17,Fevent celebrating the 50th anniversary
OL,18,Fof the King's Trust at the Royal
OL,19,FAlbert Hall, Sir Rod congratulated
OL,20,FCharles on his trip to the "Americas".
OL,26,@|D@\OU|D@eO]
