OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778598676
OL,3,CRod Stewart tells King he put 'ratbag'
OL,4,CTrump 'in his place' during state visit
OL,6,FThe singer said to the King: "May I
OL,7,Fsay, well done in the Americas. You
OL,8,Fwere superb, absolutely superb, put
OL,9,Fthat little ratbag in his place."
OL,11,FDuring the four-day state visit,
OL,12,FCharles and Camilla were hosted by
OL,13,FTrump and his wife, Melania, where the
OL,14,Fpresident showered the royals with
OL,15,Fpraise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778598676
OL,3,CRod Stewart tells King he put 'ratbag'
OL,4,CTrump 'in his place' during state visit
OL,6,FCharles was equally as gracious to his
OL,7,Fhosts, but he also did not shy away
OL,8,Ffrom discussing topics like Nato,
OL,9,FUkraine, or the environment, all
OL,10,Fissues on which the White House and
OL,11,FLondon differ.
OL,13,FLater, in a speech at a state dinner,
OL,14,Fthe King joked to his hosts that "if
OL,15,Fit wasn't for us, you'd be speaking
OL,16,FFrench!"
OL,18,FOn Monday evening, Charles appeared to
OL,19,Flaugh off Sir Rod's comment, as
OL,20,FRolling Stones guitarist Ronnie Wood
OL,21,Fgrinned next to them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
