CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778598676
OL,3,CRod Stewart tells King he put 'ratbag'
OL,4,CTrump 'in his place' during state visit
OL,6,FSir Rod appeared to continue, saying:
OL,7,F"Exactly, that's it ` it went right
OL,8,Fover his head, right over his head."
OL,10,FThe King continued the conversation
OL,11,Fbriefly, but it is unclear what he
OL,12,Freplied.
OL,14,FSir Rod then turned to Camilla and
OL,15,Ftold her: "I was just congratulating
OL,16,Fyour husband on his wonderful
OL,17,Fperformance in the Americas, so great,
OL,18,Fso brave, so proud."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
