OL,3,CRod Stewart tells King he put 'ratbag'
OL,4,CTrump 'in his place' during state visit
OL,6,FThe event at the London concert hall
OL,7,Fon Monday was a celebration of young
OL,8,Fpeople from across the UK who have
OL,9,Fbeen helped by the King's Trust youth
OL,10,Fcharity since it was founded by
OL,11,FCharles in 1976.
OL,13,FAs they arrived on the red carpet,
OL,14,FCharles and Camilla were greeted by TV
OL,15,Fpresenters Anthony McPartlin and
OL,16,FDeclan Donnelly, who were hosting the
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
