PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778598676
OL,3,CRod Stewart tells King he put 'ratbag'
OL,4,CTrump 'in his place' during state visit
OL,6,FThe King said it had been a "long
OL,7,Ftime" since he had last seen Ant and
OL,8,FDec, remarking that they did not look
OL,9,Fa day older.
OL,11,FMcPartlin, 50, replied that he had "a
OL,12,Flot of makeup on".
OL,14,FSome of the young people helped by the
OL,15,Ftrust were presented with awards by
OL,16,Fcelebrities including singer Alesha
OL,17,FDixon and Emily In Paris actress Lily
OL,18,FCollins.
